These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, reading, singing, sudoku, video-games
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, trike, bus, jet-ski, skateboard
1. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
8. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |      3       |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby   | chess    | video-games   | reading      | sudoku  | singing    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | skateboard | bus | trike | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-2::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, surfing, handball, volleyball
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, roller, snowmobile, tram
 1. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
 2. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the tram##2
11. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |      4      |   5    |
| Sport   | handball   | badminton     | cricket | surfing | volleyball    |
| Transport     | motorbike | snowmobile | jet-ski   | tram        | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, fanta, mirinda, tea
City: marseilles, liverpool, hannover, colone, san-francisco
1. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
3. the person traveling to colone is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
5. the person traveling to liverpool is the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
8. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |
| Beverage   | fanta   | cola       | tea         | almond-milk | mirinda |
| City      | hannover | liverpool | marseilles | colone   | san-francisco |

