.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-4::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, d&b, gospel, pop, salsa
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, bus, airplane, scooter, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
 2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
 3. the fan of pop is the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is the fan of pop##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 7. the person driving the bus is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 8. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
 9. the fan of salsa is in an odd position##4
10. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |    4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | gospel  | salsa   | d&b      | classical  |
| Transport   | scooter | snowmobile | skateboard | bus | airplane |

