.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-5::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bolivar, montecristo, old-henry, havana
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, rowing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the havana-smoker and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
5. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the montecristo-smoker##5
6. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |   5    |
| Cigar    | bolivar | siglo | montecristo     | old-henry     | havana |
| Sport   | skiing  | cycling   | ice-hockey | lacrosse | rowing |

