.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-6::.
There are 5 different nationalities: turkish, pakistani, british, canadian, australian
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, motorbike, taxi, van
 1. the pakistani is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 2. the australian is in an odd position##4
 3. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 4. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
 5. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the canadian##5
 8. the canadian is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the british is on the left or right of the turkish##3
10. the person driving the van is on the left of the australian##1
11. the british is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Nationality   | british | turkish | australian  | pakistani     | canadian  |
| Transport     | taxi    | van    | helicopter | motorbike | airplane |

