.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, juice, milk, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, november, august, september, june
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
5. the person drinking milk is the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
7. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2   |   3   |     4     |   5   |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | milk  | fanta | soy-milk  | juice |
| Birthday   | june          | august | september | october | november   |

