.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-8::.
There 5 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi, lemon, spinach, strawberry
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, skateboarding, soccer, cycling, tennis
1. the person eating cranberry is the person eating cranberry##1
2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
7. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating cranberry and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | lemon    | kiwi    | strawberry | cranberry | spinach   |
| Sport   | soccer | cycling | skateboarding | tennis  | badminton |

