.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-11::.
House: craftsman, cottage, wooden, tower, farmhouse
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, card-games, dancing, fishing, writing
 1. the cottage house is on the left or right of the tower house##3
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 4. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 7. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 8. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 9. the wooden house is between the craftsman house and the tower house##2
10. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |    5     |
| House   | farmhouse     | craftsman       | wooden    | tower | cottage |
| Hobby      | writing | card-games | dancing | camping | fishing  |

