.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-13::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, orange, apricot, turquise, blue
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, skateboard, train, trike
1. the person who likes turquise is between the person driving the bike and the person who likes blue##2
2. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
3. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who likes red is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
6. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
7. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
8. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |   5    |
| Color    | blue        | turquise | apricot | orange   | red |
| Transport   | skateboard | trike  | bike     | helicopter | train  |

