.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-14::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, librarian, teacher, videographer, writer
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, november, march, august, may
1. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
2. the accountant is between the teacher and the person who's birthday is in march##2
3. the writer is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
4. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
6. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
7. the librarian is the person who's birthday is in august##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is the accountant##1
9. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in august and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |    5    |
| Job   | videographer | accountant | teacher    | librarian | writer  |
| Birthday   | march       | september       | november | august  | may |

