4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching sports movies##2
6. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5
7. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4
8. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |      4      |      5      |
| Hobby   | gardening    | cooking    | card-games | dancing     | photography |
| Movie-Genre     | romance | thriller | sports    | family | spy  |

