5. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
6. the person playing poker is the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
9. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3       |     4     |    5    |
| Hobby         | hiking  | traveling | magic-tricks | skydiving | singing |
| Game   | monopoly | go   | scrabble   | chess | poker |

