.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, milk, soy-milk
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, prince, oliveros, davidoff, bongani
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the pall-mall-smoker is between the oliveros-smoker and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
5. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |      2       |     3      |      4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | milk      | soy-milk     | fanta      | coffee       | juice    |
| Cigar        | oliveros | pall-mall | prince | bongani | davidoff |

 